        "timestamp": "2018-01-10 13:41:12.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\ni think you suggested this time we will keep it as hard coded and open a jira to align all base64 authorization later.\n\nalso, because consul itself dont provide any base64 conversion replacement so we have to pass into consul pod as a part of environment variable.\n\nwe have to further explore how we achieve that later on.",
